description: Defines data models related to authentication and note management for the application, including request and response classes and the Note data model.

classes.name: AuthResponse
classes.description: Contains the access token received after successful authentication.

classes.name: Note
classes.description: Models a note, including its ID, title, content, and timestamps.

classes.name: NoteRequest
classes.description: Represents data required to create or update a note.
